  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which is the best photo editing app for Android and iPhone?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" photo editing app can depend on your specific needs, skill level, and preferences. However, some highly-rated and popular photo editing apps that are available for both Android and iPhone are:\n\n1. **Adobe Lightroom**:\n   - **Features**: Professional-grade editing tools, RAW image support, presets, and cloud syncing.\n   - **Pros**: Robust set of tools, user-friendly interface, great for both beginners and advanced users.\n   - **Cons**: Some advanced features require a subscription.\n\n2. **Snapseed**:\n   - **Features**: Wide range of editing tools, filters, and selective adjustments.\n   - **Pros**: Free to use, intuitive interface, powerful tools suitable for various skill levels.\n   - **Cons**: Lacks some advanced features found in paid apps.\n\n3. **VSCO**:\n   - **Features**: Presets for quick edits, advanced tools for manual adjustments, and a community for sharing photos.\n   - **Pros**: Great for social media enthusiasts, beautiful presets, and a user-friendly interface.\n   - **Cons**: Many advanced features and presets require a subscription.\n\n4. **PicsArt**:\n   - **Features**: Photo editing, collage maker, drawing tools, and a large library of effects and stickers.\n   - **Pros**: Versatile, great for creative projects, and a wide range of tools.\n   - **Cons**: Can be overwhelming due to the abundance of features, some advanced tools require a subscription.\n\n5. **Afterlight**:\n   - **Features**: Filters, textures, light leaks, and advanced editing tools.\n   - **Pros**: Easy to use, great for creating artistic effects, and a good balance of features.\n   - **Cons**: Some features require in-app purchases.\n\nEach of these apps has its strengths, so the best choice depends on what you're looking for in a photo editing app. If you're a beginner, Snapseed or VSCO might be a good start. If you're more advanced or looking for professional tools, Adobe Lightroom could be the best fit.",
